trators can create and define as many roles as they need, and assign their team members to them.</span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">CSV import. </span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Expand your deployment’s reach to CSV-formatted data -- one of the most flexible and ubiquitous sources around. You can now add datasets through a simple upload tool, whether they were collected years ago, manually, or from third-party services.</span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Private deployments. </span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Protect sensitive data. You can now password-protect your deployment, keeping your data and sources accessible to a select group AND secure.</span></div></li></ul><br class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Cost</span></div><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Responder is now available to </span><a href="http://www.ushahidi.com" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Ushahidi.com deployments</span></a><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class=""> for $499 per month, which includes the added capacity to store 5,000 posts and create unlimited custom Post Types. Responder features are also available to Ushahidi Open source deployments at no cost.</span></div><br class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">You can sign up or upgrade your existing open source deployment today. &nbsp;</span></div><br class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;" class=""><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Get moving with Responder today, and </span><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/issues" style="text-decoration:none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">share your feedback with us</span></a><span style="font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">.</span></div><br class=""><div style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" class=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Want to know more about how to use the Responder features? </span><a href="https://www.ushahidi.com/support" style="text-decoration: none;" class=""><span style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">Check out our user guide</span></a><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class=""> for detailed how-to and </span><a href="https://www.ushahidi.com/support/get-involved" class="">contribution guides</a><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;" class="">. You can also get in touch with us via </span><a href="http://irc.lc/freenode/ushahidi" style="text-decoration: none;" class=""><span style="c